r />\n<br />\nD人講搭山手線好過地鐵，我要成田機場一次買埋？定係東京各JR站都有得買？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我乜都唔識</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote> 同埋回程果張票我鬼知應該搭咩時間既班次<br />\n因為回程 9:40機 要預早幾多點起身 之後去邊搭反NEX去成田？</blockquote><br />\n問埋啲問題真係好撚弱智<br />\n依家你去旅行，連預幾多時間都唔識，咪撚做人啦<br />\n仲有，乜撚叫鬼知撘咩時間班次<br />\n時刻表JR官網有㗎屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote> 真心唔知回程果張票點玩法，如果要我買來回時要計定時間搭咩班次 我遲左味冇左張票，同埋即時唔知搭咩車返成田，到時香港都唔識返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </blockquote><br />\n你on9就咪撚學人去旅行喇，機票咪一樣冇撚得改，乜撚野叫咩玩法啊，book reserved seat 係咁㗎啦<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote> D人講搭山手線好過地鐵，我要成田機場一次買埋？定係東京各JR站都有得買</blockquote><br />\n屌你老母，上網check都有啦，撚知你要去邊咩，點知邊樣方便啊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote> 我乜都唔識</blockquote><br />\n大撚曬啊？咪撚去囉乜都唔識"},{"pid":"c6b46c9caa3819bc52ff28303ffb6c26a9416b5c","tid":284200,"uid":9412,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T18:18:34.000Z","msg":"完美展示垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfac31a1f2b44fca2a4a9bee046fdeb0b0d39af8","tid":284200,"uid":25148,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T18:57:29.000Z","msg":"你連中文都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dfd6d18b90c4a74e32c4b9c8919737f894876c2","tid":284200,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T00:17:55.000Z","msg":"去台灣好過"},{"pid":"3a0ffc94d8e242c04a471fff474c147c8cfe005e","tid":284200,"uid":34553,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T00:23:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去台灣好過</blockquote><br />\n可能台北捷運都唔識搭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3123d03a8d1700cb0255d0434cfc5bf4f9fc8e6","tid":284200,"uid":34553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2